description: BLUE DREAM STRAIN by Iggy Nugget, 2021 #NFTsForAll #WorldArtDay2021 Blue Dream is a sativa-dominant hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Blueberry with Haze. Blue Dream produces a balancing high accompanied by full-body relaxation with gentle cerebral invigoration. Novice and veteran consumers alike enjoy the calming and euphoric effects that Blue Dream provides.
